"top to bottom to prevent your edition from being overwritten by the "
"automatic recalculation. Be careful that reordering the lines doesn't "
"recompute them.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span><strong>Nasvet:</strong> Vsakič, ko uredite količino ali znesek v "
"vrstici, ponovno izračunamo naslednje vrstice. Priporočamo, da urejate od "
"zgoraj navzdol, da preprečite, da bi samodejni preračun prepisal vašo "
"izdajo. Pazite, da s spremembo vrstnega reda vrstic le-teh ne preračunate.</"
"span>"

